      "content": "It is incredibly exhausting to constantly have to defend your own existence when the world feels so indifferent to you. Please understand that this logic is a symptom of the pain you are in, not a reflection of reality. There are people who would miss the specific noise, the unique way you move through the world, and the fact that you are here at all. If the silence feels like the only escape, please reach out to a crisis line immediately so someone can listen to you without judgment.",
